      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
