      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is free of tears or odors, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button and feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent brake fluid flush and oil change performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. This is a reliable, honest car ready for its next chapter. Includes two sets of keys, a full service history log, and a set of weather-resistant floor mats.",
      "price": 34500.0,
